Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.78,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}貴方以上なんていないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}You're my missing piece
